                     <interp inst="t17740112-56-off292" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17740112-56-off292" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing four pair of silver shoe buckles, value 30 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17740112-56-victim532" type="victimName">
                     William
                      Bird
                  <interp inst="t17740112-56-victim532" type="surname" value="Bird"></interp>
