            </rs>, <rs id="t17740112-56-punish299" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17740112-56-punish299" type="punishmentCategory" value="transport"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17740112-56-defend530 t17740112-56-punish299"></join>
               T
            </rs>. </p>
